  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] as a Polish citizen [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] during one of these night sessions with KGB, incidentally, there was a little glimpse of hope there too because the guy that was, well, you in America call it interviewing, but it wasn't exactly interviewing.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it wasn't torturing either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] pressuring or-- the word will come to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It turned out from KGB-- turned out that, that he gave a hint to my father that he is a Jew, and he will try to help my father.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then when he started pushing my father, both physically and verbally, my father says, take it easy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, I'm a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that apparently gave the other guy a clue or whatever that they have to free my father according to the new agreement with the British.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they let go of my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by that time, he couldn't walk because he, he could not-- he didn't walk for three or four months, the time that he was in jail, so his knees were stiff.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He looked terribly decrepit, so I went with him to the barber shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He needed a shave and a haircut, and he still had his old uniform from the hospital even though underneath he had civilian, civilian clothing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went for a haircut, and from there, he went to officer's club to, to get some bread with the same uniform-- with the same coat on top without uniform underneath.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Obviously, had they discovered that he wasn't working for the Russians anymore in any way, they would have probably sent him back to Siberia for good now, never seen the daylight, but they didn't.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
